data.description: AMAZING PRICE IMPROVEMENT!! Amazing fixer that needs a little love awaits you in gorgeous, sought after Steilacoom! 4 bdrm, 2 3/4 baths, fenced yard and the list goes on. Remodeled kitchen where all appliances stay. Slider off kitchen. Gas stove/electric is available. Remodeled master bath. Lower level has an amazing second master/MIL/bonus room along with a jetted tub & shower behind brick wall area (but can be reversed & used). Cat5 internet throughout the entire home. Upgraded with A/C! New roof under a yr old. Sold AS-IS.  Inspection Report available! PLS EXCUSE MESS- SELLERS IN PROCESS OF MOVING! Home will be cleaned & empty prior to closing.
